---
import Button from '~/components/ui/Button.astro';
---

<section class="relative bg-brand-black text-white py-24 lg:py-32 overflow-hidden">
 <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-0">
   <img
     src="/images/hero/charity-bg.svg"
     alt="The plumber paradox"
     class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-75"
     loading="lazy"
   />
   <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-black/80 via-black/60 to-black/30"></div>
 </div>

 <div class="container-x relative z-10 max-w-3xl">
   <div class="flex items-center gap-6 mb-8">
     <span class="font-display text-2xl tracking-tight font-medium">PURIST</span>
     <span class="text-white/40">×</span>
     <span class="text-xs tracking-wider uppercase border border-white/30 rounded-full px-3 py-1.5">
       The Plumber Paradox
     </span>
   </div>

   <p class="eyebrow text-white/70 mb-4">Why free tools need paid experts</p>
   <h2 class="font-display text-h1 mb-6 text-balance">
     The tools are free. <em class="font-medium">The expertise is not.</em>
   </h2>
   <p class="text-base lg:text-lg text-white/80 mb-10 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl text-pretty">
     n8n is free. Make is almost free. YouTube has unlimited tutorials. So why do businesses
     pay $5,000+? Because 56% of SMBs lack anyone capable of using these tools.
     A business owner can learn n8n in 40 hours or pay us to have it running in a week.
     It's the same reason plumbers charge $150/hour despite free YouTube tutorials.
   </p>

   <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 lg:gap-8 mb-10 max-w-xl">
     <div>
       <p class="font-display text-3xl lg:text-4xl">56%</p>
       <p class="text-xs text-white/70 mt-1">of SMBs lack internal expertise</p>
     </div>
     <div>
       <p class="font-display text-3xl lg:text-4xl">40h</p>
       <p class="text-xs text-white/70 mt-1">to learn it yourself</p>
     </div>
     <div>
       <p class="font-display text-3xl lg:text-4xl">5 days</p>
       <p class="text-xs text-white/70 mt-1">for us to deploy it</p>
     </div>
   </div>

   <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
     <Button href="/pages/contact-us" variant="secondary" class="bg-white text-brand-black border-white hover:bg-transparent hover:text-white">
       Book a free audit →
     </Button>
     <a href="/pages/blog" class="inline-flex items-center text-sm underline underline-offset-4 hover:opacity-80 self-center">
       Read the full story →
     </a>
   </div>
 </div>
</section>
